DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260523T040000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261026T040000Z
UID:Block by Block-2026-05-23 04:00:00+00:00
DESCRIPTION:May 23–October 25\, 2026\n\nFor 30 years\, theGreenest Block
  in Brooklyn contesthas demonstrated how small collective actions can buil
 d communities and transform neighborhoods\, block by block. Celebrate this
  anniversary with special exhibits and events.Learn More›about Block by 
 Block\n\nMore info:\nhttps://www.bbg.org/blockbyblock\n\n<img src="/img/up
 loads/manual/hero/_list_thumbnail_regular/2026_BbB_Web_1120x744_RR1.png" a
 lt="" />
LOCATION:Brooklyn Botanic Garden\, 990 Washington Ave\, Brooklyn\, NY 1122
 5
END:VEVENT
